-- Chalco, Rio Tinto to Sign Agreement on Guinea Project, Securities Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-29T00:07:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/chalco-rio-to-sign-deal-on-guinea-iron-ore-project-securities-reports.html

          
          
             Aluminum Corporation of China Ltd.
and Rio Tinto Group will sign an agreement for development of a
large iron-ore mine in Guinea today, the Shanghai Securities
News reported, without saying where it got the information.  
